<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Aureuma API Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #f6f3ea;
        --panel: #fffdf7;
        --ink: #1f2421;
        --muted: #56615c;
        --line: #d8d1c2;
        --accent: #0b6b57;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(11, 107, 87, 0.08), transparent 28rem),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #f9f6ee 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
        color: var(--ink);
      }

      main {
        max-width: 48rem;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 1.25rem 4rem;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--panel);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(31, 36, 33, 0.08);
      }

      h1, h2 {
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      p, li {
        line-height: 1.65;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      ul {
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding: 0.3rem 0.65rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(11, 107, 87, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .meta {
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
        padding-top: 1rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      a {
        color: var(--accent);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</div>
        <h1>Aureuma API Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>
          This page describes how Aureuma handles information sent to API endpoints hosted at
          <strong>nucleus.aureuma.ai</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2>What this service does</h2>
        <p>
          This service accepts authenticated API requests and returns API responses needed to operate
          an Aureuma-hosted integration.
        </p>

        <h2>Information we process</h2>
        <p>When you use this service, we may process:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>request content you send to the API;</li>
          <li>response content returned by the API;</li>
          <li>technical metadata such as timestamps, request identifiers, and status codes;</li>
          <li>authentication data needed to validate access to the service.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How we use information</h2>
        <p>We use this information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>authenticate and authorize API access;</li>
          <li>operate, maintain, and secure the service;</li>
          <li>debug failures, investigate abuse, and improve reliability;</li>
          <li>keep records needed for service continuity and auditing.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell API request data. We may share data only with infrastructure or service
          providers that help us host, secure, or operate this service, or when required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain API data and service logs only for as long as reasonably needed for operations,
          security, legal compliance, and troubleshooting.
        </p>

        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>
          We use reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational measures designed to protect
          the service and the information processed through it.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy questions about this service, contact
          <a href="mailto:privacy@aureuma.ai">privacy@aureuma.ai</a>.
        </p>

        <p class="meta">Effective date: 2026-04-15</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
